@startuml
title Use Case Diagram Sistem Iuran PGRI

left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

' Actors
actor "Kabupaten" as kabupaten
actor "Admin" as admin

' System Boundary
rectangle "Sistem Iuran PGRI" {
  
  ' Shared Use Cases
  usecase "Login" as login
  usecase "Logout" as logout
  
  ' Kabupaten Use Cases
  usecase "Lihat Dashboard\nKabupaten" as dashboard_kab
  usecase "Bayar Iuran" as bayar
  usecase "Lihat Riwayat\nTransaksi" as riwayat_kab
  usecase "Lihat Laporan\nIuran" as laporan_kab
  
  ' Admin Use Cases
  usecase "Lihat Dashboard\nAdmin" as dashboard_admin
  usecase "Lihat Riwayat\nTransaksi (All)" as riwayat_admin
  usecase "Kelola Notifikasi" as notifikasi
  usecase "Buat Laporan" as laporan_admin
  usecase "Kelola Data\nKabupaten" as kelola_kab
  
  ' Extension Use Cases
  usecase "Lihat Detail\nTransaksi" as detail
  usecase "Lanjutkan\nPembayaran" as lanjut
  
  ' Include relationships (dari use case ke Login)
  dashboard_kab ..> login : <<include>>
  dashboard_admin ..> login : <<include>>
  
  ' Extend relationships (dari extension use case ke base use case)
  detail ..> riwayat_kab : <<extend>>
  lanjut ..> riwayat_kab : <<extend>>
  detail ..> riwayat_admin : <<extend>>
  riwayat_kab ..> bayar : <<extend>>
}

' Actor to Use Case relationships - Kabupaten
kabupaten --> login
kabupaten --> dashboard_kab
kabupaten --> bayar
kabupaten --> riwayat_kab
kabupaten --> laporan_kab
kabupaten --> logout

' Actor to Use Case relationships - Admin
admin --> login
admin --> dashboard_admin
admin --> riwayat_admin
admin --> notifikasi
admin --> laporan_admin
admin --> kelola_kab
admin --> logout

' Notes
note right of bayar
  Kabupaten melakukan pembayaran
  melalui payment gateway.
  Sistem memproses pembayaran
  secara otomatis di backend.
end note

note right of riwayat_admin
  Admin memonitor semua transaksi
  dari seluruh kabupaten.
  Tidak ada verifikasi manual.
end note

note bottom of login
  **Use Case Shared:**
  Login digunakan oleh kedua aktor.
  Sistem akan redirect ke dashboard
  sesuai dengan role pengguna.
end note

@enduml
